</P>
<P>
	ISTANBUL, Turkey (AP) -- Only one day after an arson attack  
killed 13, a bomb blast under a truck here killed at least one 
person and wounded five others today, media reports said. Explosive 
experts defused a second bomb planted inside a crowded Burger King 
fast-food restaurant on the outskirts of the city, the Anatolia 
news agency said. Private Star television said the fatal blast 
under the truck occurred in a low-income district, Bahcelievler. 

</P>
