off feisty Mississippi 74-66 today in the second round of the 
Midwest Regional. It was the 20th straight victory for the Spartans 
(31-4). In other play, Kentucky beat Kansas 92-88 in overtime, 
Miami of Ohio upset Utah 66-58, and Southwest Missouri State got an 
81-51 win over Tennessee. 

