<HEADLINE> Best-Selling Books </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	WALL STREET JOURNAL BEST SELLING BOOKS   	
</P>
<P>
	FICTION   	
</P>
<P>
	1. ``The Testament'' by John Grisham (Doubleday)  
</P>
<P>
	2. ``River's End'' by Nora Roberts (Putnam)  
</P>
<P>
	3. ``Ashes to Ashes'' by Tami Hoag (Bantam)  
</P>
<P>
	4. ``Single &AMP; Single'' by John le Carre (Scribner)  
</P>
<P>
	5. ``Tara Road'' by Maeve Binchy (Delacorte)  
</P>
<P>
