<HEADLINE> Sununu Co-chairing Quayle Campaign </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	WASHINGTON (AP) -- Sen. Spencer Abraham of Michigan and former  
White House chief of staff John Sununu are members of former Vice 
President Dan Quayle's national co-chairs for his 2000 presidential 
campaign, the campaign said Sunday. 
